  "name": "MERIT DEM: Multi-Error-Removed Improved-Terrain DEM",
  "description": "Webpage for the MERIT DEM (Multi-Error-Removed Improved-Terrain Digital Elevation Model) dataset. MERIT DEM is a high-accuracy global digital elevation model at 3 arc-second resolution (~90 m at the equator), developed by removing multiple error components from existing spaceborne DEMs. The site provides information about the dataset, download instructions, licensing, and citation information.",
